.bd
.ti -5
NAME
.br
repeat - followed by a decimal number and a command will
result in repetition of the command the stated number of times.

.ti -5
.bd
SYNTAX
.br
repeat ### command ...

.ti -5
.bd
DESCRIPTION
.br
The maximum number is 65535 but a command line such as
"repeat 10 repeat 10 date" would repeat a date command 100
times.  This utility is useful for system testing
and exercising.

.ti -5
.bd
EXAMPLE
.br
repeat 100 fsck -n -t /dev/root
